front.title: •Don't Do That Again (V)
front.gametext: Plays on table. Always Thinking With Your Stomach, Ice Storm, and Sandwhirl are canceled. Once per game, may take an Immediate Effect into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. Unless opponent occupies a battleground system, Mobilization Points is suspended.
front.lore: The Jedi won't tolerate silly behavior for very long.

pulls: The Time For Our Attack Has Come
What're You Tryin' To Push On Us?
